## 💡 How to Use This Prompt

| Scenario | How to apply |
|---|---|
| **AI-assisted migration** | Paste this prompt + attach your `pom.xml` and runner class |
| **File-by-file review** | Add `"Here is the file: [paste code]"` at the bottom |
| **Full project scan** | Append a zip/file tree and ask it to list all affected files first |
| **Incremental migration** | Use each numbered section as a standalone sub-prompt |
